N2  - Abstract Withdrawal: Does Higher Energy Efficiency Lower Economy-Wide Energy Use? Sebastian Rausch and Hagen Schwerin. The above article from the International Economic Review, published online on 20 January 2019 in Wiley Online Library (wileyonlinelibrary.com) as an Accepted Article (https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/abs/10.1111/iere.12388), has been withdrawn by agreement between the journal's Co-Editor Masaki Aoyagi, and Wiley Periodicals, LLC. The withdrawal has been agreed following a recommendation by the authors? institution, ETH Zurich, due to an unresolved authorship dispute.
